nor-quest <nqrlf> makes bid for northair <nrm.to>
    nanaimo, british columbia, april 13 - 
nor-quest resources inc said it will make a takeover offer to acquire
all shares of northair mines ltd on the basis of one nor-quest share
plus one dlr for two shares of northair. nor-quest said it plans to
bring northair's willa mine in the nelson area of british columbia
into production using nor-quest's recently acquired 1200-ton per day
mill located in the area. reuter 
